<ul>
<FONT size=3 face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#8b1a1a"><p>I will be busy the next few days, and then visiting family members one after the other for a week or so, and will not have a chance to update the site for a week or more.</p><p>I want to take this opportuntiy to wish all the readers and contributers of this site a very Merry Chistmas (or whatever holiday you celebrate).</p><p>In the last 3 months, this has become the #1 website for Monks, and it has been YOU that has made it great. Not me, YOU. Without the support, via submissions, message board and chat room, even down to people spreading word of the site within the game and by word of mouth, it would never have become the giant that it has.</p><p>This is Zadkiel, signing off until next week.</p></FONT></ul>

